The,service,maintains,a,geographic,information,database,of,historical,information,related,to,placenames,in,China,The,placenames,are,cross,referenced,by,spelling,variants,comprising,or,more,records,referring,to,more,than,locations,including,places,significant,in,Chinese,history,Information,provided,documents,historical,events,linked,to,the,places,specified,API,methods,support,queries,against,the,same,database,accessed,by,search,tools,on,the,CHGIS,website,Queries,can,specify,placenames,as,romanized,ASCII,strings,of,UTF,encoded,Chinese,characters,either,simplified,or,complex,glyphs,Responses,can,be,limited,for,particular,date,ranges,if,desired